Title: Debate Extracts Evaluation 1
Description: Help us compare different extracts from online debates for use in summaries
Answer.abortion-layout_v_layout_random-c: While A had a few nonsensical phrasings sprinkled throughout, B is clear only intermittently. For one example: Under the "Common points" section, we read, "Life begins at birth and abortion." This doesn't make sense and it is therefore doubtful it was ever commonly used. B isn't trustworthy.
